<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff; 
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: auto;
      margin-top: 50px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .text-primary {
      color: #007bff;
    }
    .text-danger {
      color: #e74c3c;
    }
    img {
      width: 300px;
      height: 400px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    table {
      margin-top: 20px;
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    th, td {
      padding: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
    }
    th {
      text-align: left;
      width: 30%;
    }
    .form-control {
      width: 70%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #007bff;
      border-color: #007bff;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
      border-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
  <title>Toy Detail</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container col-md-8 text-center mt-3 mb-3">
    <a href="/lego" class="btn btn-primary mb-3">Toy List</a>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <img src="{{lego.image}}" alt="lego">
        <h5 class="text-primary mt-3">{{lego.name}}</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <h1 class="text-danger">Toy Detail</h1>
        <table class="table table-bordered">
          <tr>
            <th>Price</th>
            <td>{{lego.price}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Quantity</th>
            <td>{{lego.quantity}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Description</th>
            <td>Products are certified 2009/48/EC and ED 71 on the level of toy safety and international toy standards ASTM F963-2008, so they absolutely do not contain harmful substances harmful to children. The Schleich characters are meticulously modeled down to the last detail, carefully hand-drawn and providing educationally valuable playtime.
Shadow Lion - 42555 is a haunting new threat stalking EldradorÂ®. As dark as night, the Shadow Lion's silhouette bears a resemblance to the fearsome Lava Lion you've seen before. Possessing an extremely scary dark magic.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th colspan="2">
              <form action="/lego/legoOrder" method="post" >
                <input class="form-control mb-3" type="number" name="quantity" min="1" max="{{lego.quantity}}" required>
                <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{lego._id}}">
                <input type="hidden" name="price" value="{{lego.price}}">
                <input class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-left: 160px;" type="submit" value="Add to cart">
              </form>
            </th>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
